          <p class='first-para'>
            It is not exactly the same but it is an educational function. It is worth looking at. I am pleased that the Minister has been able to give this a general welcome but I am slightly disappointed in other respects. We must look at the wording and try to table an amendment that gives more oomph to what the Charity Commissioner does. In the mean time, I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.</p><p>
